    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    DynamicController
    REST controller for handling dynamic air quality data notifications
    DynamicControllerTest
    Unit tests for DynamicController.
    DynamicReading
    A class to represent dynamic site data.
    DynamicReadingDTO
    Data Transfer Object for deserialsing each site's actual environmental metrics (ie pollution data and timestamp) json data received from Flask web service
    DynamicReadingRepository
    Repository interface for accessing and managing dynamic data entities
    DynamicReadingRepositoryTest
    Unit tests for DynamicReadingRepository.
    DynamicReadingService
    Service layer for managing dynamic reading entities
    DynamicReadingServiceTest
    Unit tests for DynamicReadingService.
    NgrokConfig
    Configuration class for storing NGROK URLs used in the application.
    NotificationDTO
    Data Transfer Object for deserialsing incoming notification block of json data received from Flask web service
    PollutionPushPayloadDTO
    Data Transfer Object for deserialsing top level incoming json data received from Flask web service
    PollutionSubscriber
    Component that runs on start up to subscribe for pollution data updates every 60 seconds
    Site
    A class to represent static air monitoring site metadata.
    SiteController
    REST controller for managing Site entities.
    SiteMetadataDTO
    Data Transfer Object for deserializing static site metadata received from external Flask web service.
    SiteReadingDTO
    Data Transfer Object for deserialsing site level json data ie system code number and list of environmental metrics received from Flask web service
    SiteRepository
    Repository interface for accessing and managing Site entities.
    SiteRepositoryTest
    Unit tests for SiteRepository.
    SiteService
    Service layer for managing Site entities.
    SpringapiApplication
    Spring API for PANT MSc Software Development Dissertation
    StaticSiteDataLoader
    Component that runs on application startup to fetch static site metadata from the web service and synchronize it with the database.
